  apply AESTronglyMeasurable.comp
  В· -- Show that g is AESTronglyMeasurable
    exact stronglyMeasurable_g
  В· -- Show that RCLike.im is continuous
    apply Continuous.continuous
    apply RCLike.continuous_im
  В· -- Show that Real.toNNReal is continuous
    apply Continuous.continuous
    apply Continuous.toNNReal
  В· -- Show that NNReal.toReal is continuous
    apply Continuous.continuous
    apply Continuous.toReal
```

Wait, actually `gвӮғ` is `fun x вҶҰ Real.toNNReal (RCLike.im (g x))`.
So `gвӮғ = Real.toNNReal вҲҳ RCLike.im вҲҳ g`.

The `AESTronglyMeasurable` proof would be:
`apply AESTronglyMeasurable.comp`
`В· exact stronglyMeasurable_g` (for `g`)
`В· exact continuous_RCLike_im` (for `RCLike.im`)
`В· exact continuous_toNNReal` (for `Real.toNNReal`)

Then, `T' gвӮғ = T (gвӮғ)`. The proof that `T' gвӮғ` is `AESTronglyMeasurable` is `T_meas gвӮғ hf3`.

Finally, `enorm вҲҳ T' gвӮғ` is `norm вҲҳ T' gвӮғ`. Since `T' gвӮғ` is `AESTronglyMeasurable` and `norm` is continuous, `norm вҲҳ T' gвӮғ` is `AESTronglyMeasurable`.

The full proof term would be:
```tactics
apply AESTronglyMeasurable.comp
В· -- Show that T' gвӮғ is AESTronglyMeasurable
  apply T_meas gвӮғ
  -- Proof that gвӮғ is AESTronglyMeasurable
  apply AESTronglyMeasurable.comp
  В· -- Show that g is AESTronglyMeasurable
    exact stronglyMeasurable_g
  В· -- Show that RCLike.im is continuous
    apply Continuous.continuous
    apply RCLike.continuous_im
  В· -- Show that Real.toNNReal is continuous
    apply Continuous.continuous
    apply Continuous.toNNReal
В· -- Show that norm is continuous
  apply Continuous.continuous
  apply Continuous.norm
